# **PRD + Build Blueprint**

## Product: **Snap2Sheet**

---

# 1. **Core Product Definition (PRD)**

## 1.1 Product Goal

Convert an image into **structured, exportable CSV data** in under 10 seconds.

---

## 1.2 Core User Loop (this is everything)

> Capture → Extract → Review → Export

If this loop is smooth, product works.
If this loop breaks, product is useless.

---

## 1.3 MVP Feature Set (LOCK THIS)

* camera capture
* gallery upload
* OCR extraction (via backend)
* structured field detection
* editable review screen
* CSV export
* share file
* local history

No more features. Don’t add.

