# 3. **API Contract (Backend)**

Keep this VERY simple.

---

## **POST /extract**

### Request

```json
{
  "image": "base64 or file upload"
}
```

---

### Response

```json
{
  "rawText": "full OCR text here",
  "documentType": "invoice",
  "fields": {
    "vendor": "ABC Store",
    "date": "2026-04-18",
    "totalAmount": "2450",
    "tax": "18%"
  },
  "lineItems": [
    {
      "name": "Item 1",
      "quantity": "2",
      "price": "500",
      "amount": "1000"
    }
  ]
}
```

---

## CSV Generation (frontend or backend)

Example:

```
Vendor,Date,Total,Tax
ABC Store,2026-04-18,2450,18%
```

