# 4. **Extraction Logic (Important)**

Pipeline:

1. OCR → raw text
2. raw text → structured fields (AI or regex)

Example prompt logic (if using LLM):

> Extract vendor name, date, total amount, and tax from this text. Return JSON.

Keep it strict.

