# 9. **Definition of Done (IMPORTANT)**

App is done ONLY IF:

* full flow works end-to-end
* no crashes in normal usage
* export works reliably
* user can complete task without confusion
* UI doesn’t look like dev tool
* installable build works on real phone

---

# 10. **Big Mistakes to Avoid**

* adding login
* adding too many document types
* chasing perfect OCR
* overengineering backend
* redesigning UI again and again
* not testing on real device

